question: Within 110 kilometers, which fast food restaurant can I find from Chatham Square, New York, NY on the way to Dyckman Farmhouse Museum, New York, NY?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.998531 40.713506)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.922886 40.867382)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.998531 40.713506)',4326)::geography, 110000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.998531 40.713506)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
